Photo by Memes.com on September 20, 2021. May be a meme of 3 people and text that says 'When you buy a charger from a shady store 90% 90% 89% MEMES'.
Photo by Memes.com on September 19, 2021. May be an image of food and text that says 'We all have that one friend who still eats like this'.
Photo by Memes.com on September 19, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'poorly drawn cats @poorlycatdraw aspiring goth bimbo @sadsexybat to be fair that's a poorly shaped cat'.
Photo by Memes.com on September 18, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'In a pre game lobby and your friends skin glitches back to default'.
